data.description: Discover your dream home in this meticulously crafted 2016 Craftsman Modern residence, seamlessly blending classic charm with contemporary design. The open-concept floor plan invites you into a gourmet kitchen equipped with state-of-the-art appliances, sleek countertops, and ample storage, perfect for both chefs and entertainers. Sunlit rooms showcase craftsman-style trim and warm hardwood floors, enhancing the sense of space and sophistication. The master suite, a true sanctuary, features a spa-like bathroom: dual showers and spacious walk-in closet, while additional bedrooms offer flexibility for guests or a home office. Step outside to a meticulously landscaped low maintenance yard, extending your living space to a patio and private backyard. 3 car garage with storage. Conveniently located in Harris Ranch, this home provides easy access to Boise foothills, river, and greenbelt. With modern design and timeless craftsmanship, this Craftsman Modern gem isn't just a house; it's a lifestyle waiting for you.
